# Language Boundaries

- Code and machine artifacts are in English (identifiers, constants, keys, schema fields, comments/docstrings).
- Requirement specs under `spec/requirements/` are in German with correct umlauts/`ß`.
- Technical docs under `doc/` may be German or English, but keep one consistent primary language per document.
